#Setting default ssh host on Linux
1. sudo vim /etc/hosts
2. inside hosts file, this file is the DNS resolver for linux:

 #ows instances
 <ip-name> tab   <alias>
 10.93.68.147    bf2_1
 10.93.68.227    bf2_2
 10.93.70.168    bf2_3

3. ssh bf2_1 

4. use linux alias to even shorten command more... 
